metadata.description:
7000 x 7000px
Ai Art
Curated by Anna Dart with Superchief Gallery NFT for AI Surrealism 2023

Jennifer Panepinto aka QuantumSpirit is a visual artist combining analog and digital processes, using a range of mediums from Polaroid to AI Art. Her artworks are inspired by her own journey with mental health, exploring both positive and dark concepts, frequently using rainbows.
